title: DC SHOES: REDISCOVER THE ROAD -- MIKE MO
description:
When you're on your first skate trip with a new team, you never know what to expect. But some of the best times can be had on the road, especially when you're traveling with a tight crew. After the three week Rediscover Oz tour, and Mike Mo's first trip with Chris Cole, Mikey Taylor, Nyjah Huston, Matt Miller, Wes Kremer, Evan Smith and DC, Mo's rediscovered the best of what the road has to offer. 

Featuring: Mike Mo Capaldi, Chris Cole, Mikey Taylor, Matt Miller, Nyjah Huston, Wes Kremer, Evan Smith, flow rider Kyle Frederick, and DC Australia team riders Kieran Reilly, Bugs Fardell, Casey Ainsworth, Deon Williams, Marty Girotto, Jake Hayes. 

Music Credits:
Guards
"Do It Again"
Rediscover DC at http://www.dcshoes.com/us/en/skate
